# Demo Honesty

ChatCRM **MVP 1** = beli putus (single tenant). When Supabase is configured, **auth + DB persistence are real**. WhatsApp inbox and billing remain simulated unless stated otherwise.

## What is real (when Supabase configured)

- Email/password login (Supabase Auth)
- Owner invite flow → email → set password
- Customer/message/agent data persisted in PostgreSQL
- RFM / CLV / cadence calculations (client-side logic, real customer data from DB)

## What is simulated (say so in UI if adding related features)

| Feature | Reality |
|---------|---------|
| WhatsApp inbox | Mock messages — not connected to WA Business API |
| Export CSV | Toast + audit log — verify file download before claiming |
| Billing settings | Placeholder UI — not Stripe/payment |
| Demo login shortcuts | Labeled dev/demo — pre-filled credentials |

## MVP 1 auth copy

- **No** "Daftar sekarang" — use *"Hubungi owner bisnis Anda"*
- **No** public registration route
- Invite flow is production-intent for deployed instances

## Do not add without explicit ask

- Public SaaS signup / multi-tenant org picker
- Fake loading spinners for instant in-memory ops
- "Production-ready" WhatsApp webhooks
- Marketing landing copy inside authenticated app

## If user asks for SaaS phase

Plan separately: organizations, subscriptions, self-serve register — see `mvp1-product.mdc`.
